{"tid":689453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"佔旺案庭內拍攝】官令唐琳玲付逾19萬訟費　扣除還押日子","createTime":"2018-06-04T05:51:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T08:32:39.000Z","uid":13663,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"10531a67f13443787447f7622cf6a60a6d3f21e0","tid":689453,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T05:51:18.000Z","msg":"佔旺案庭內拍攝】官令唐琳玲付逾19萬訟費　扣除還押日子　唐明獲釋 (13:38)<br />\n2018/6/4<br />\n<br />\n律政司起訴17人於2014年在佔旺清場期間涉違反禁制令，控方早前讀出開案陳辭時，內地女子唐琳玲被指在庭內拍攝，她因未有依時交出保釋金，其後被捕，法官陳慶偉今裁定唐琳玲罪成，判唐監禁7天。"},{"pid":"a0ba8bac6c89c63f2b868a5680f0d6d3eaef6c15","tid":689453,"uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T05:51:48.000Z","msg":"律政司向陳官申請，要求唐支付逾19萬元訟費。唐拒絕支付，認為費用是不合理及不合法，又認為律政司一方大律師的收費「跟我沒有關係，黃大律師是應律政司邀請，並不是我邀請」。但陳官認為律政司收費合理，並是唐多番拒絕由大律師或法援代表。<br />\n<br />\n陳官下令唐支付律政司197,260元訟費，形容該些相片非常昂貴，希望唐下次能更有智慧處理事件。唐回應「try to be（盡力而為）」。陳官散庭前，特別感謝大律師艾勤賢的協助。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，扣除還押日子，唐琳玲仍須服刑一天，故將於明天才獲釋。"},{"pid":"09b7b56b25c7678d0d01d60195ca97cf3881a562","tid":689453,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T05:53:05.000Z","msg":"又走20萬數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acf707cdd9573f991a1015035c1b5117da899230","tid":689453,"uid":445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T05:53:31.000Z","msg":"有冇人開post賭唐琳玲找數就裸跑"},{"pid":"36c1989366496d72e831d7a3c4e21e1c9d27dc58","tid":689453,"uid":13492,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T05:53:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不要緊，你還有党呀</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"610d35016ed6bdada621b9702a372f38be2f82b8","tid":689453,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T05:53:59.000Z","msg":"法庭好好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"63aa0922037737c052d10b0ef15bdc610bf08181","tid":689453,"uid":6347,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T05:56:22.000Z","msg":"點解無廢老話佢搞搞振<br />\n成班老而不死，淨係針對後生仔"},{"pid":"d02e67e6cc879f9b9b861609e677c2394661faa1","tid":689453,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"acf707cdd9573f991a1015035c1b5117da899230","tid":689453,"uid":445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T05:53:31.000Z","msg":"有冇人開post賭唐琳玲找數就裸跑"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T05:57:13.000Z","msg":"今次就穩陣好多，因為肯定佢唔會俾錢"},{"pid":"75ee9e06c67b4027e54f30c62df9c8944f6f32a8","tid":689453,"uid":34410,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"63aa0922037737c052d10b0ef15bdc610bf08181","tid":689453,"uid":6347,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T05:56:22.000Z","msg":"點解無廢老話佢搞搞振<br />\n成班老而不死，淨係針對後生仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T05:57:17.000Z","msg":"YAHOO D廢老潛哂水<br />\n今次單野太柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed7c258ee64a52a9805678c39d8e7a2e8b95eb5f","tid":689453,"uid":103325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T05:59:13.000Z","msg":"唔找數就收鳩咗佢張身份證，以後唔俾嚟香港"},{"pid":"8850a83748a9d6af446f7141b1a3d8117d713f7a","tid":689453,"uid":12568,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d02e67e6cc879f9b9b861609e677c2394661faa1","tid":689453,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"acf707cdd9573f991a1015035c1b5117da899230","tid":689453,"uid":445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T05:53:31.000Z","msg":"有冇人開post賭唐琳玲找數就裸跑"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T05:57:13.000Z","msg":"今次就穩陣好多，因為肯定佢唔會俾錢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T05:59:58.000Z","msg":"想知唔比錢出唔出到境？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{